            "DisplayOrder": 330,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7800,
            "LocalizeKR": "저만을 위한\n특등석이랄까… 후훗…",
